  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, upon rolling initiative, roll a 1d4.</p><p> For a number of rounds equal to the result, you and your Puppet gain a +15 bonus to movement speed, a +1 to AC, and advantage on the first attack roll either of you make per round.</p><p> Also at 6th level, you learn the E-Rank Ninjutsu Chakra Blow.</p><p> When you take the Attack action, as long as you hit with at least 1 attack with the Attack action, you can cast Chakra Blow as part of the same action, affecting your final attack that hits.</p><p></p>",
